{
  "stem": "11179.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is now in Frankfurt, before I was five years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I always had all the toys I ever wished for.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe not as many as others, but I-- I wasn't-- there was no-- no-- no need.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I remember that I was a happy child.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] One incident, is-- which has been probably influenced my life negatively, I remember I-- my parents went, usually Saturday afternoons, to cafe house, which was-- in Europe, cafe house was entertainment.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had musicians there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was relaxing, stay a couple of hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you could take kids along.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A lot of these cafe houses had-- had-- had two rooms, one with music, one without.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and I-- I liked music, evidently, even as a kid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was going in front of this little three or four piece combo, and was conducting him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And one drummer gave me a little conducting stick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And one day, a man played a cello, and I'll never forget that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He used his bow, and just tipped me on the head.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "For him, it was funny, but he didn't smile.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I screamed and ran away, and never did this again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I think I became shyer from that time on, but I don't know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it stands out in my mind as some-- as something bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't think the man meant any bad, to be quite sure.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Berlin, there were some.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of them were not.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived in Berlin in-- in a middle class neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like I said, there were about four or five Jewish kids living in-- in-- in the complex where we lived, and we had a huge backyard there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we-- about the size of two football fields.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
